title: The Illuminati - On Borrowed Time (2004)
description:
After listening to "On Borrowed Time," you&#039;d be forgiven for thinking the Illuminati come from somewhere south of the Mason-Dixon Line. Actually, they&#039;re from the Great White North: Toronto. But you&#039;d never know it by the way the group sounds: It&#039;s a highly electric Southern boogie/rock hybrid that flirts with punk-rock brevity and even some jazzy finesse.
